data.description: This home features 1200 sq ft, 3 bdrm, 2 bath built in 2019 only 4 years old. Great for hosting family events this home has an open floor plan with the kitchen, dining, and living rooms interconnected. Master bedroom has room for a king-sized bed and still is spacious with a large walk in closet. The floor plan has parental privacy to the large 2nd & 3rd bedrooms. Enjoy the solitude of the backyard with a 6ft privacy fence and no other homes built behind it.
